Welcome to my Portfolio! This is a showcase of my skills, projects, and journey as a web developer. The portfolio is designed to highlight my expertise in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and to provide a glimpse into the work I’ve done so far.

Features
About Me: A brief introduction about who I am, my passion for web development, and my interests.

Projects: A collection of projects I’ve worked on, including descriptions and technologies used.

Contact Form: A simple and interactive form to get in touch with me for collaborations, job opportunities, or just to say hello!

Technologies Used
HTML: For structuring the content of the portfolio.

CSS: For styling and making the portfolio visually appealing.

JavaScript: For adding interactivity, such as form validation or dynamic content.

Purpose
This portfolio serves as a platform to:

Showcase my skills and projects.

Demonstrate my ability to create clean, responsive, and user-friendly websites.

Provide a way for potential employers or collaborators to contact me.

How to Use
Navigate through the sections using the navigation menu.

Explore the Projects section to see my work.

Use the Contact Form to send me a message.
